      <b data-is-speakable>'Good And Mad' Explores Women's Anger At A Pivotal Moment</b>   <b data-is-speakable>It hardly needs saying that women's anger (more from one political party) has been roiling since the 2016 election. Rebecca Traister's new book explores the history and politics involved.</b>
